data.description:
Open house Saturday Dec 16 12:00pm-2:00pm. 

Welcome to 1466 Plymouth Rock Way. This amazing 2 bed/2 bath condo is ready for rental move in. As you enter you are greeted with ample natural light and vaulted ceilings. The kitchen fits perfectly adjacent to the living room. The two car garage attached to the home is conveniently located for unloading groceries into the kitchen. Both bedrooms have fans and spacious closets. Enjoy some time outside on your private patio off the master bedroom, in the front yard in the green belt, or at the nearby Rotary Park on the corner.

12 month lease
